phase2.explanation:
You forgot @FXML annotation on the field!

Without @FXML, the field is private and not accessible by FXMLLoader.

FIX: Add @FXML:
@FXML
private Label label;

Also add @FXML to event handler methods:
@FXML
private void handleEvent() { ... }

Always use @FXML for all fields and methods that interact with FXML!

